<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١١٦:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {يُطَافُ عَلَيْهِمْ بِكَأْسٍ مِنْ مَعِينٍ <span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> بَيْضَاءَ لَذَّةٍ لِلشَّارِبِينَ <span class="c2">(٤٦)</span> لَا فِيهَا غَوْلٌ وَلَا هُمْ عَنْهَا يُنْزَفُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٧)</span>} <span class="c4">[الصافات: ٤٥ - ٤٧]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{غَوْلٌ}</span>: <span class="c2">«وَجَعُ البَطْنِ»</span>،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{يُنْزَفُونَ}</span>: <span class="c2">«لاَ تَذْهَبُ عُقُولُهُمْ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>